import React from "react";
import { Link as RouterLink } from "react-router-dom";
import {
  Box,
  Button,
  Chip,
  Container,
  Grid,
  Paper,
  Stack,
  Typography,
} from "@mui/material";
import { alpha, useTheme } from "@mui/material/styles";

function Badge({ children, color = "primary", size = 36 }) {
  const theme = useTheme();
  const bg = alpha(theme.palette[color]?.main || theme.palette.primary.main, 0.12);
  const fg = theme.palette[color]?.main || theme.palette.primary.main;
  return (
    <Box
      sx={{
        display: "inline-flex",
        alignItems: "center",
        justifyContent: "center",
        width: size,
        height: size,
        borderRadius: 1.25,
        bgcolor: bg,
        color: fg,
        fontWeight: 800,
        flex: "0 0 auto",
      }}
    >
      {children}
    </Box>
  );
}

function Landing() {
  const theme = useTheme();
  const subtleBg = alpha(theme.palette.primary.main, theme.palette.mode === "dark" ? 0.15 : 0.08);

  return (
    <Box component="main" sx={{ bgcolor: "background.default", color: "text.primary" }}>
      {/* Hero */}
      <Box component="section" sx={{ py: { xs: 6, md: 10 } }}>
        <Container maxWidth="lg">
          <Grid container spacing={4} alignItems="center">
            <Grid item xs={12} md={7}>
              <Stack spacing={2.5}>
                <Chip
                  label="Cr√©ditos en l√≠nea"
                  color="primary"
                  variant="soft"
                  sx={{ alignSelf: "flex-start", fontWeight: 700 }}
                />
                <Typography component="h1" variant="h2" fontWeight={800} lineHeight={1.1}>
                  Obt√©n tu pr√©stamo en minutos
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="h6" color="text.secondary">
                  Solicita cr√©dito r√°pido, seguro y sin papeleo. Todo 100% online,
                  con tasas transparentes y respuesta inmediata.
                </Typography>
                <Stack direction="row" spacing={1.5} flexWrap="wrap">
                  <Button
                    component={RouterLink}
                    to="/register"
                    variant="contained"
                    size="large"
                  >
                    Solicitar ahora
                  </Button>
                  <Button
                    component={RouterLink}
                    to="/login"
                    variant="outlined"
                    size="large"
                  >
                    Simular pr√©stamo
                  </Button>
                </Stack>
              </Stack>
            </Grid>

            <Grid item xs={12} md={5}>
              <Paper
                elevation={3}
                sx={{
                  p: 3,
                  borderRadius: 3,
                  background: `linear-gradient(135deg, ${alpha(
                    theme.palette.primary.light,
                    0.18
                  )} 0%, ${alpha(theme.palette.info.light, 0.18)} 100%)`,
                }}
                aria-hidden
              >
                <Stack spacing={2.5}>
                  <Stack direction="row" spacing={1.5} alignItems="flex-start">
                    <Badge color="success">‚úì</Badge>
                    <Box>
                      <Typography fontWeight={700}>Aprobaci√≥n al instante</Typography>
                      <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                        Sin filas, sin papeleo, sin complicaciones.
                      </Typography>
                    </Box>
                  </Stack>

                  <Stack direction="row" spacing={1.5} alignItems="flex-start">
                    <Badge>üí≥</Badge>
                    <Box>
                      <Typography fontWeight={700}>Desembolso a tu cuenta</Typography>
                      <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                        R√°pido y seguro.
                      </Typography>
                    </Box>
                  </Stack>

                  <Stack direction="row" spacing={1.5} alignItems="flex-start">
                    <Badge color="warning">‚ö°</Badge>
                    <Box>
                      <Typography fontWeight={700}>Proceso 100% digital</Typography>
                      <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                        Disponible 24/7.
                      </Typography>
                    </Box>
                  </Stack>
                </Stack>
              </Paper>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Container>
      </Box>

      {/* C√≥mo funciona */}
      <Box component="section" sx={{ py: { xs: 6, md: 8 } }}>
        <Container maxWidth="lg">
          <Box sx={{ textAlign: "center", mb: 3 }}>
            <Chip label="¬øC√≥mo funciona?" color="primary" variant="soft" />
            <Typography variant="h4" fontWeight={800} mt={1.5}>
              Tu cr√©dito en 3 pasos
            </Typography>
          </Box>
          <Grid container spacing={2}>
            {[
              {
                n: "1",
                title: "Completa tu solicitud",
                text: "Reg√≠strate y dinos cu√°nto necesitas.",
              },
              { n: "2", title: "Aprobaci√≥n al instante", text: "Respuesta inmediata." },
              { n: "3", title: "Dinero en tu cuenta", text: "Desembolso seguro." },
            ].map((s, i) => (
              <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4} key={i}>
                <Paper variant="outlined" sx={{ p: 2.5, borderRadius: 2 }}>
                  <Stack direction="row" spacing={1.5} alignItems="center">
                    <Badge size={40}>{s.n}</Badge>
                    <Box>
                      <Typography variant="subtitle1" fontWeight={700}>
                        {s.title}
                      </Typography>
                      <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                        {s.text}
                      </Typography>
                    </Box>
                  </Stack>
                </Paper>
              </Grid>
            ))}
          </Grid>
        </Container>
      </Box>

      {/* Beneficios */}
      <Box component="section" sx={{ py: { xs: 6, md: 8 }, bgcolor: "background.paper" }}>
        <Container maxWidth="lg">
          <Box sx={{ textAlign: "center", mb: 3 }}>
            <Chip label="Beneficios" color="primary" variant="soft" />
            <Typography variant="h4" fontWeight={800} mt={1.5}>
              Todo lo que necesitas
            </Typography>
          </Box>
          <Grid container spacing={2}>
            {[
              { icon: "üìù", title: "Sin tr√°mites complicados", text: "Proceso simple y guiado." },
              { icon: "‚ö°", title: "Respuesta inmediata", text: "Decisi√≥n en minutos." },
              { icon: "üíπ", title: "Tasas transparentes", text: "Sin costos ocultos." },
              { icon: "üåê", title: "100% online", text: "Desde cualquier dispositivo." },
            ].map((b, i) => (
              <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3} key={i}>
                <Paper variant="outlined" sx={{ p: 2.5, borderRadius: 2 }}>
                  <Stack direction="row" spacing={1.5} alignItems="center">
                    <Badge size={44}>{b.icon}</Badge>
                    <Box>
                      <Typography variant="subtitle1" fontWeight={700}>
                        {b.title}
                      </Typography>
                      <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                        {b.text}
                      </Typography>
                    </Box>
                  </Stack>
                </Paper>
              </Grid>
            ))}
          </Grid>
        </Container>
      </Box>

      {/* Confianza / Seguridad */}
      <Box component="section" sx={{ py: { xs: 6, md: 8 } }}>
        <Container maxWidth="lg">
          <Box sx={{ textAlign: "center", mb: 3 }}>
            <Chip label="Confianza" color="primary" variant="soft" />
            <Typography variant="h4" fontWeight={800} mt={1.5}>
              Tu seguridad es primero
            </Typography>
          </Box>

          <Stack spacing={1.5}>
            <Stack direction="row" spacing={1.5} alignItems="flex-start">
              <Badge color="success">üõ°Ô∏è</Badge>
              <Typography>
                <Box component="strong">Tus datos est√°n protegidos.</Box> Utilizamos buenas
                pr√°cticas de seguridad.
              </Typography>
            </Stack>
            <Stack direction="row" spacing={1.5} alignItems="flex-start">
              <Badge color="info">üéì</Badge>
              <Typography>
                <Box component="strong">Proyecto acad√©mico</Box> ‚Äî Simulaci√≥n de microservicios para
                fines educativos.
              </Typography>
            </Stack>
            <Stack direction="row" spacing={1.5} alignItems="flex-start">
              <Badge color="warning">üß™</Badge>
              <Typography>
                <Box component="strong">Simulaci√≥n sin compromiso:</Box> puedes probar el flujo sin
                afectar datos reales.
              </Typography>
            </Stack>
          </Stack>
        </Container>
      </Box>

      {/* Llamado final */}
      <Box component="section" sx={{ py: { xs: 6, md: 8 }, bgcolor: subtleBg }}>
        <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ textAlign: "center" }}>
          <Typography variant="h4" fontWeight={800} mb={1}>
            Simula tu pr√©stamo ahora
          </Typography>
          <Typography color="text.secondary" sx={{ mb: 2.5 }}>
            Conoce tus opciones en minutos. Es r√°pido, seguro y 100% online.
          </Typography>
          <Stack direction="row" spacing={1.5} justifyContent="center" flexWrap="wrap">
            <Button component={RouterLink} to="/register" variant="contained" size="large">
              Comenzar
            </Button>
            <Button component={RouterLink} to="/login" variant="outlined" size="large">
              Ya tengo cuenta
            </Button>
          </Stack>
        </Container>
      </Box>

      {/* Footer */}
      <Box component="footer" sx={{ py: 3, borderTop: 1, borderColor: "divider" }}>
        <Container maxWidth="lg">
          <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary" textAlign="center">
            ¬© {new Date().getFullYear()} Cr√©ditos Financieros ‚Äî Proyecto acad√©mico. Sin fines
            comerciales.
          </Typography>
        </Container>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default Landing;
